%% Log/data flow (Mermaid)
flowchart LR
    A[Attacker 192.168.1.30] -->|TCP attack| B[Container :808x]
    B -->|JSON to stdout| C[Docker json-file driver]
    C -->|tail /var/lib/docker/containers/&lt;id&gt;/&lt;id&gt;-json.log| D[Filebeat]
    D -->|autodiscover + decode_json_fields| E[processors: lab_id, shipper, host metadata]
    E -->|TCP 5044 Beats/Lumberjack v2| F[Logstash :5044]
    F --> G[flatten honeypot.* object]
    G --> H[coerce types int/bool]
    H --> I[GeoIP enrich src_ip]
    I --> J[derive attack_class from attack_type_hint]
    J --> K[drop noisy fields]
    K --> L[Elasticsearch index honeypot-logs-YYYY.MM.dd]
    L --> M[Kibana dashboards :5601]
    L --> N[ML ingest 01_ingest.py scroll]
    N --> O[data/raw.parquet]
    O --> P[02_features.py]
    P --> Q[data/features.parquet]
    Q --> R[03_train.py]
    R --> S[models/*.joblib]
    S --> T[04_evaluate.py]
    T --> U[trained_models/]
